title: Furnished 2.5 Bedroom in Cute Duplex
map_address: Halifax Ave N near Halglo place
posting_body: ['Available October 1 (possibly earlier, between 9/17 and 10/1).', 'This furnished 2BD + bonus room/office is in a side by side duplex.', 'Attached 1 car garage, central air, balcony, dishwasher, microwave, backyard deck, and laundry in unit at no extra charge!', '1 block from a park, basketball court, pond and walking trails.', '1 minute to highway 100 (36th street exit) or Theo Wirth Parkway.', '4 blocks from North Memorial Hospital.', '800 square feet.', 'Note: one bedroom is small- about 9X10, but has 2 closets.', 'A queen bed fits just fine.', 'The other bedroom is 10X12 and is currently being used as an office, but a king bed could fit (but it’s a little tight).', 'Finished bonus room in the basement is about 9X9 and a good office or storage room, with small closet.', 'If you like to garden there is space in the yard and planters on the balcony.', ':)', 'Awesome neighbors.', 'Quiet street.', 'Application fee $25 per adult applicant, must be able to pass a background check.', '$1395/month with $1395 deposit.', 'Utilities not included- they tend to run $200/month total (approx.', '$50/month each for internet, electric, gas and water depending on your usage).', 'Downtown Robbinsdale restaurants and breweries are 5 minutes away.', 'Not set up for section 8.', 'Pet friendly but yard not fenced in.', 'Tenant pays all utilities.', 'Tenant responsible for lawn/yard care and snow removal (driveway only).']
